channel.title: [REQ]Website
channel.description:
Hey guys. I have come here to ask all you web designers to try to make me a site. I am asking for the following things
Style: Something like pwnds.info, only red themed. Theme: Red, [url=http://www.1001freefonts.com/winfonts/mael.zip]Mael[/url] font. Logo Style: same as pwnds.info, only saying io9Labs in red and in Mael font. Buttons: Same as pwnds.info, only Red+Mael font. Button Roll-over:Same as above only background of nutton becomes yellow. Any other Requests: PSD's for the Logo, buttons, and button roll-overs if possible.
I was hoping if anyone can do this for free, and feel free to put "Designed by -yournamehere- for io9Labs".
